Summary: Witness observed strange "aircraft" overflying Green Bay, Wisconsin
divs: Sighting DetailsThe Witness was outside in his backyard when he heard the sound of what he thought was a commercial jet airliner, but the sound was different. When he looked up, he was surprised to see what appeared to be a large commercial sized aircraft with another smaller aircraft grafted to the nose of the large aircraft. He noted that he could see no engines or engine necelles. The aircraft was a dark gray color, almost the same color as the overcast which gave it a ghostly appearance. It seemed to gain altitude, and was lost from view as it blended into the overcast. Although lost from view, he could still hear it as it moved from the Northwest to the Southeast.
